        <div class="container">

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1 col-sm-push-6  col-sm-6">
                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h2 class="section-heading">Auto Generate Playlists</h2>
                    <p class="lead">Auto Generate related songs based on what you listen to most often. <br><br> Enjoy classical piano? Automatically generate the next best songs for your playlist with a single click. <br><br>Need an hour of workout music, pick your favourite pump up song and <b>auto generate</b>.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-pull-6  col-sm-6">
                    <div class="discover"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- /.container -->

    </div>

